# Pipeline run-state artifacts (sample tracking JSON etc.) generated at
# runtime should be written to the scratch/store directories used by the
# pipeline scripts, not committed to the repo. If one lands here by mistake,
# ignore it instead of committing it.
*_deleteme*

# Allow GUI application image assets (logo, icons, status indicators) even though
# generated output figures elsewhere in the repo (e.g. statistics plots) are ignored above.
!BrainBeam/gui/images/*.png
!BrainBeam/gui/images/*.PNG
